nodes.text: CT-66-3233 was a cadet and part of Bravo Squad.

When ARC trooper Commander Colt arrived on Kamino to supervise the graduation tests of the clone cadets, Bravo Squad was the first team to take the Citadel Challenge. During this challenge, the cadets worked as a team and finished the course in record time, with Domino Squad watching them from above. When it was time for Domino to take the test, this clone mocked them, telling his squad to watch as the team fails.

This Bravo Squad cadet's identification number was first depicted in the episode "Clone Cadets" of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. It says 66-3233, and the prefix CT- was predetermined. This way of determining identification numbers was proved with the troopers in Domino Squad.
